A good breakfast is not only packed with carbs or starch but should also be packed with proteins. Most Kenyans love avocado and would incorporate it with other meals from time to time. But with this new recipe, you might just want to include it in your first meal of the day. For this method, you can have your eggs four ways; scrambled, fried, boiled or poached to top off your avocado. It is simple to make, tasty and satisfying. Ingredients Preparation Step 1 (Optional) In a pan over medium heat, put the slices and heat until a little crunchy. Step 2 In a bowl, put the avocado slices and mash with a fork. Season with salt and pepper to your liking Step 3 Spread the avocado on the toasted bread Step 4 Step 5 Place your egg on the avocado toast and enjoy with a cup of coffee or juice. Tips for making this recipe